": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 24, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8413420, "raw_content": "Federal judges \u2014 including those appointed by different presidents \u2014 were asked to authorize release of grand jury materials and related documents so the DOJ could comply with the law. The DOJ filed motions asking judges in the Southern District of New York to lift protective orders on this material. \n\nBondi was not delaying the releases. She was getting judicial approval. Nobody here is defending her, but Massie knows better. \n\nOther judges asked to review release motions include Paul A. Engelmayer, who rejected lawmakers\u2019 request for a special monitor to force faster disclosure. The DOJ was instructed NOT TO RELEASE FILES without judicial approval over every page. ", "author": "HorrorGameDev", "created": 1770836056108, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "blockchain-the-vote", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Thomas Massie can't be trusted. He's adopted his wife's leftism. He's not ONCE criticized the Clinton & Obama judge overseeing the Epstein files", "last_comment_created": 1770836155180, "content": "<p>Federal judges \u2014 including those appointed by different presidents \u2014 were asked to authorize release of grand jury materials and related documents so the DOJ could comply with the law. The DOJ filed motions asking judges in the Southern District of New York to lift protective orders on this material.</p>\n<p>Bondi was not delaying the releases. She was getting judicial approval. Nobody here is defending her, but Massie knows better.</p>\n<p>Other judges asked to review release motions include Paul A. Engelmayer, who rejected lawmakers\u2019 request for a special monitor to force faster disclosure. The DOJ was instructed NOT TO RELEASE FILES without judicial approval over every page.</p>\n", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 25, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}], "status": true}